data.description: Prime Location in the Heart of Valrico! This exquisite 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom townhouse boasts 1635 sq. ft. of living space and comes with a convenient 2-car garage. Nestled within the highly coveted Savannah Landings private gated community, this home reflects a true sense of pride in ownership and boasts a NEW ROOF! Step inside and discover an inviting open floor plan that seamlessly connects with natural paint choices and large windows. A spacious kitchen features beautiful cabinets with crown, skylight, and a breakfast bar. The combination of the formal dining and great room creates the perfect space for entertaining. The thoughtful layout features a split-plan bedroom configuration, ensuring privacy and versatility. The primary suite features large windows and a private en-suite with a garden tub, separate walk-in shower, and spacious walk-in closet! Two additional bedrooms offer flexibility as potential office, den, or hobby spaces, and storage throughout the home ensures clutter-free living. Notable features include a laundry room with a sink, a 2-car garage for your convenience, and a delightful screened-in back patio perfect for unwinding. The roof was recently replaced in 2021, providing added peace of mind. The community itself is impeccably maintained and offers residents access to a refreshing pool and clubhouse. Plus, you'll find yourself just a short distance away from grocery stores and restaurants, making everyday errands a breeze. Current furniture is optional in the sale of the home. Don't miss this opportunity! Schedule an appointment to view this fantastic property and experience the exceptional lifestyle it offers. Your search for the perfect home ends here! View the home virtually with this link: my.matterport.com/show/?m=EeVDh5iJv8t&mls=1
